{
  "stem": "23645.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think there's three or four of us that, that survived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, when we finished the public school, we went-- I went to cheder.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was a different kind of life, again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At the public school, again, after this incident, I was on my guard.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when they had the Lord's Prayer-- they had more than the Lord's Prayer.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had a religious service.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so, us Jewish kids would be excused.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we would go out for three quarters of an hour and play on the-- in the hallways.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because we didn't want to-- you know, we had this-- at least that privilege, to let us out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And don't forget, it was mainly Catholic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that's the reason I got beaten up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because the liturgy on Sunday school when they went was very, very [NON-ENGLISH], you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was-- very, very anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And you know, only till recently it was still in there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Not so many years ago, it was still-- And, to this day, I think some of these Eastern countries are still-- you know, I was, I was shattered when I saw the for instance.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he interviewed these Poles that-- the Jews have-- have disappeared from Poland!",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And, and you see still the, the imprint of the mezuzah in the doors.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they talk about the Jews-- oh, how wonderful that they disappeared, that they killed them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They should have killed all of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You would think that, after all these years, that there would be a little bit of, of feeling left in the Poles, and say-- and a little bit of compassion.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But it's not there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After school, there was a violin-- a violin-- in our house.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think my older-- my two brothers were pretty good at  it.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
